## Price Formatting by Locale

```jsx
const formatPrice = (amount, lang) => {
  return new Intl.NumberFormat(
    lang === 'bg' ? 'bg-BG' : 'en-US',
    { style: 'currency', currency: 'EUR' }
  ).format(amount)
}
```

